OL,7,FProsecutor Craig Jones said after
OL,8,Fmeeting online, the defendant and
OL,9,Fvictim subsequently met in person.
OL,11,FHe said the victim thought he was "a
OL,12,Flittle odd" and a bit "touchy-feely"
OL,13,Fon the first date, but added she
OL,14,Fdecided to give him the benefit of the
OL,15,Fdoubt and they continued seeing each
OL,16,Fother at weekends.
OL,18,FThe court heard Henry told the woman
OL,19,Fhe worked away a lot, in a job in gas
OL,20,Fmarine engineering.
