OL,8,Fthe course of the relationship, with
OL,9,Fthe defendant aware she had left the
OL,10,Fwoman some money in the will.
OL,12,FHenry continually "pestered" the woman
OL,13,Ffor money over the following months,
OL,14,Fmaking threats to kill himself if she
OL,15,Fdid not.
