OL,7,FThe 33-year-old then used her phone to
OL,8,Ftransfer money into his own account.
OL,10,FMr Jones said the victim tried to end
OL,11,Fthe relationship following the breach
OL,12,Fof trust, but the defendant
OL,13,F"manipulated" her into continuing.
OL,15,FThe court heard after months of
OL,16,Fcontrolling behaviour, including
OL,17,Fmonitoring the woman's social media
OL,18,Faccounts and whereabouts, Henry used
OL,19,Fdog trimmers to cut off some of the
OL,20,Fwoman's hair in August last year.
