OL,11,FIn a statement read to the court by
OL,12,Fthe prosecutor, the woman described
OL,13,Fher time with the defendant as
OL,14,F"horrendous," adding she had been
OL,15,Fisolated from family and friends.
OL,17,FShe said during the course of the
OL,18,Frelationship he had taken roughly
