OL,7,FLouis Henry, of Clos y Gelyn, Pentwyn,
OL,8,FCardiff, had previously pleaded guilty
OL,9,Fto engaging in coercive or controlling
OL,10,Fbehaviour, assault occasioning actual
OL,11,Fbodily harm (ABH) by cutting off the
OL,12,Fwoman's hair, and assault by beating
OL,13,Fin an incident which had seen him
OL,14,Fcatching the woman with an open hand
OL,15,Fin the doorway of her house.
OL,17,FHe has previous convictions including
OL,18,Fthe harassment of a previous partner
OL,19,Fand burglary.
