OL,7,FWith a one-sixth reduction for his
OL,8,Fguilty pleas Henry was sentenced to 30
OL,9,Fmonths in prison comprising 30 months
OL,10,Ffor the controlling behaviour, four
OL,11,Fmonths for the ABH, and seven days for
OL,12,Fthe battery all to run concurrently.
OL,14,FHenry will serve up to half of the 30
OL,15,Fmonths in custody before he is
OL,16,Freleased on licence to serve the rest
OL,17,Fin the community.
